<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>iteration on 6cdh's Blog</title><link>https://6cdh.github.io/tags/iteration/</link><description>Recent content in iteration on 6cdh's Blog</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>en</language><lastBuildDate>Wed, 07 Oct 2020 11:54:55 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://6cdh.github.io/tags/iteration/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>递归转换为迭代的通用技术</title><link>https://6cdh.github.io/posts/recursion-to-loop/</link><pubDate>Wed, 07 Oct 2020 11:54:55 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://6cdh.github.io/posts/recursion-to-loop/</guid><description>&lt;p>递归 &lt;em>(Recursion)&lt;/em> 和迭代 &lt;em>(Iteration)&lt;/em> 是等价的, 任何的递归算法都可以转换成循环, 任何迭代都可以转换成递归. 如果说到将递归转换成迭代的技术, 两种常见的方法是尾递归和模拟运行时栈.&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>